@startuml {MODULE_NAME} Architecture

!define ORCHESTRATOR #lightblue
!define AGENT #lightgreen
!define TOOL #lightyellow
!define DATA #lightgray

title {MODULE_NAME} Module Architecture

package "System Components" {
  [Orchestrator] ORCHESTRATOR
  [{MODULE_NAME} Agent] AGENT
  [External Tools] TOOL
  [Data Storage] DATA
}

' Communication flows (orchestrator-only pattern)
Orchestrator --> Agent : sends requests
Agent --> Orchestrator : returns responses
Agent --> Tool : uses tools
Agent --> Data : reads/writes data

' Notes explaining the architecture
note right of Agent
  Communicates ONLY with orchestrator
  Never directly with other agents
  Follows hub-and-spoke pattern
end note

note bottom of Orchestrator
  Central coordination point
  Manages all agent interactions
  Maintains session state
end note

' Example data flow
note as DataFlow
  **Data Flow Example:**
  1. User request → Orchestrator
  2. Orchestrator → {MODULE_NAME} Agent
  3. Agent processes using tools
  4. Agent → Orchestrator (results)
  5. Orchestrator → User (response)
end note

@enduml